      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence and round-off error contributions must be quantified and shown to be negligible relative to discretization error at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error was not assessed. Residual convergence criteria were applied but iterative error was not formally quantified or separated from discretization error. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
