      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used for validation must be drawn from production-representative devices with documented traceability to manufacturing specifications.",
      "rationale": "Test samples were prototype units; traceability to production manufacturing specifications was not documented. Sample-to-sample variability not characterised. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
