      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between validation experiment input parameters and COU input parameters must be formally demonstrated through a documented parameter mapping with quantified differences.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between the validation experiment and the VAD COU was not formally assessed. Differences in rotational speed range and fluid temperature between validation and COU were noted but not quantified. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
